title: UNREGISTER_RAW_NUI_CALLBACK
content:
0x7FB46432// UnregisterRawNuiCallback
void UNREGISTER_RAW_NUI_CALLBACK(char* callbackType);Parameters:callbackType: The callback type to targetWill unregister and cleanup a registered NUI callback handler.Use along side the REGISTER_RAW_NUI_CALLBACK native.
